name: Talisman
description: Talisman is a pioneering DeFAI (Decentralized Finance + AI) wallet, designed to transform crypto wallets from passive storage into intelligent, yield-generating engines. By combining secure self-custody with autonomous AI agents, Talisman helps users grow their portfolios through automated strategies. The $SEEK token powers this ecosystem, aligning incentives between users, developers, and agents while capturing value from protocol activity. The token is called SEEK because Talisman is built for Seekers, guiding Seekers on their journey, helping them unlock yield, opportunity, and autonomy while securing their safety.
